opposite direction with regard to the equivalent shift from
previous works. These results suggest that our improved
cosmological parameter estimates are not sensitive to
pathological misrepresentations of photometric sources by the
spectroscopy used for direct redshift calibration and,
therefore, that this systematic effect cannot be responsible for
