WFIRST. In addition, our simulations show that to limit the bias
of {\ensuremath{\Delta}}R/R and {\ensuremath{\Delta}}e in the
H158 band to {\ensuremath{\sim}}10\% of the estimated WFIRST
error budget, the quadratic NL model parameter
{\ensuremath{\beta}} must be calibrated to
{\ensuremath{\sim}}1\% and {\ensuremath{\sim}}2.4\%,
respectively. We present a fitting formula that can be used to
estimate WFIRST detector NL requirements once a true PSF error
budget is established.}},
